msgid "User activation"
msgstr "Aktivasi pengguna"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:849,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:849
msgid ""
"Send an email to every newly registered user with an activation link that "
"must be clicked to activate their account."
msgstr ""
"Kirimkan email ke setiap pengguna yang baru terdaftar dengan tautan aktivasi "
"yang harus diklik untuk mengaktifkan akun mereka."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:850,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:850
msgid ""
"There is an \"Activation status\" column under \"Users\", where you can "
"manually set the status to active/inactive and resend the activation email."
msgstr ""
"Terdapat kolom \"Status aktivasi\" di bawah \"Pengguna\", di mana Anda dapat "
"mengatur status secara manual menjadi aktif/tidak aktif dan mengirim ulang "
"email aktivasi."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:857,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:857
msgid ""
"Enable to require user to verify the email after registration through an "
"activation link."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan untuk meminta pengguna memverifikasi email setelah pendaftaran "
"melalui tautan aktivasi."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:858,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:858
msgid ""
"This feature affects all new user registrations, not just those submitted "
"via the Form element."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ini memengaruhi semua pendaftaran pengguna baru, tidak hanya yang "
"dikirimkan melalui elemen Formulir."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:863,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:863
msgid "Auto login after activation"
msgstr "Masuk otomatis setelah aktivasi"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:864,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:864
msgid ""
"Enable to automatically log the user in after successful email verification."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan untuk secara otomatis memasukkan pengguna setelah verifikasi email "
"berhasil."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:868,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:868
