msgstr "Tersedia melalui pintasan keyboard & menu konteks klik kanan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1658,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1658
msgid "Insert element"
msgstr "Sisipkan elemen"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1666,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1666
msgid "Available via \"+\" action icon & right-click context menu."
msgstr "Tersedia melalui ikon tindakan “+” & menu konteks klik kanan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1678,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1678
msgid "Available via \"Layout\" action icon."
msgstr "Tersedia melalui ikon tindakan “Tata Letak”."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1683,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1683
msgid "Import pasted images/SVGs"
msgstr "Impor gambar/SVG yang ditempel"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1685,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1685
msgid ""
"When pasting elements from another site that contain image or SVG files, "
"placeholders are used by default. Enable to download the image from the "
"source site. If the current user lacks SVG upload permissions, a placeholder "
"SVG is used."
msgstr ""
"Saat menempel elemen dari situs lain yang berisi file gambar atau SVG, "
"placeholder digunakan secara default. Aktifkan untuk mengunduh gambar dari "
"situs sumber. Jika pengguna saat ini tidak memiliki izin unggah SVG, "
"placeholder SVG akan digunakan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1686,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1686
msgid ""
"Only applies to Image, Image Gallery, and SVG elements. Images will not be "
"imported if the source is a custom URL or a dynamic data tag."
msgstr ""
"Hanya berlaku untuk elemen Gambar, Galeri Gambar, dan SVG. Gambar tidak akan "
"diimpor jika sumbernya adalah URL kustom atau tag data dinamis."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1697,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1697
msgid ""
"Set to load %s in the builder to improve compatibility in older browsers. "
"Not recommended to enable for modern browsers due to potential performance "
"impact."
msgstr ""
"Atur untuk memuat %s di pembangun untuk meningkatkan kompatibilitas di "
"browser lama. Tidak disarankan untuk diaktifkan pada browser modern karena "
"potensi dampak kinerja."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1708,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1708
msgid ""
"Enable if you experience issues loading the builder in combination with "
"Cloudflare Rocket Loader."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan jika Anda mengalami masalah saat memuat pembangun dalam kombinasi "
"dengan Cloudflare Rocket Loader."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1717,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1717
msgid "Max results"
msgstr "Hasil maksimum"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1719,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1719
msgid ""
"Maximum number of results to display for each query loop in the builder. "
"Applies only to Bricks-native queries. Leave blank to use the default value."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah maksimum hasil yang ditampilkan untuk setiap loop kueri di pembangun. "
"Hanya berlaku untuk kueri asli Bricks. Biarkan kosong untuk menggunakan "
"nilai default."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1725,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1725
msgid "Show query loop type"
msgstr "Tampilkan tipe loop kueri"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1726,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1726
msgid ""
"Display the object type (e.g. \"acf_related_writers\", \"mb_page-to-user\") "
"in the query loop type dropdown."
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan tipe objek (mis. “acf_related_writers”, “mb_page-to-user”) di "
"dropdown tipe loop kueri."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1737,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1737
msgid "Render dynamic data text on canvas"
msgstr "Render teks data dinamis di kanvas"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1738,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1738
msgid ""
"Enable to render the dynamic data text on the canvas to improve the preview "
"experience."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan untuk merender teks data dinamis di kanvas untuk meningkatkan "
"pengalaman pratinjau."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1743,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1743
msgid "Disable WordPress custom fields in dropdown"
msgstr "Nonaktifkan bidang kustom WordPress di dropdown"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1744,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1744
msgid ""
"Set for better in-builder performance. Using dynamic data tags like "
"{cf_my_wordpress_field} is still possible."
msgstr ""
"Atur untuk kinerja pembangun yang lebih baik. Menggunakan tag data dinamis "
"seperti {cf_my_wordpress_field} masih dimungkinkan."

