#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2395,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2408
msgid ""
"Review all Code element (PHP & HTML), SVG element (code), Query editor, and "
"\"echo\" tag instances."
msgstr ""
"Tinjau semua elemen Kode (PHP & HTML), elemen SVG (kode), editor Query, dan "
"instance tag “echo”."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2750,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2763
msgid ""
"Click the button above to retrieve all Code element, SVG element (code), "
"Query editor, and \"echo\" tag instances and review the code for every page, "
"template, etc."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol di atas untuk mengambil semua elemen Kode, elemen SVG (kode), "
"editor Query, dan instance tag “echo” dan tinjau kode untuk setiap halaman, "
"template, dll."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2401,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2414
msgid ""
"Please review all code instances found on your site page by page to ensure "
"they don't contain any malicious or faulty code. Click on the title to edit "
"the page, template, etc. with Bricks."
msgstr ""
"Harap tinjau semua instance kode yang ditemukan di situs Anda halaman per "
"halaman untuk memastikan mereka tidak mengandung kode yang berbahaya atau "
"salah. Klik pada judul untuk mengedit halaman, template, dll. dengan Bricks."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2405,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2418
