msgstr "Tidak valid"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2699,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2712
msgid "Reviewed"
msgstr "Ditinjau"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2713,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2726
msgid "Function names"
msgstr "Nama fungsi"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2714,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2727
msgid "Function names must pass the check through the %s filter."
msgstr "Nama fungsi harus lulus pemeriksaan melalui filter %s."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2716,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2729
msgid ""
"Copy and paste the code below into your Bricks child theme to allow those "
"functions to be called through the \"echo\" tag. Remove the function names "
"you don't want to allow. Explore the %s documentation for more code examples "
"such as using regex for more flexible echo tag checks, etc."
msgstr ""
"Salin dan tempel kode di bawah ini ke dalam tema anak Bricks Anda untuk "
"memungkinkan fungsi-fungsi tersebut dipanggil melalui tag “echo”. Hapus nama "
"fungsi yang tidak ingin Anda izinkan. Jelajahi dokumentasi %s untuk contoh "
"kode lainnya seperti menggunakan regex untuk pemeriksaan tag echo yang lebih "
"fleksibel, dll."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2757,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/code.php:73,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/code.php:185,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/svg.php:79,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2770,
#: ../includes/elements/code.php:73, ../includes/elements/code.php:185,
#: ../includes/elements/svg.php:79
msgid "Code execution"
msgstr "Eksekusi kode"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2758,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2771
msgid "Allow specific user roles or individual users to execute code."
msgstr ""
"Izinkan peran pengguna tertentu atau pengguna individual untuk mengeksekusi "
"kode."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2775,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2788
msgid ""
"Code execution has been explicitly disabled by the %s filter. This filter is "
"currently overriding your Bricks settings."
msgstr ""
"Eksekusi kode telah secara eksplisit dinonaktifkan oleh filter %s. Filter "
"ini saat ini mengesampingkan pengaturan Bricks Anda."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2781,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2794
msgid "Enable code execution"
msgstr "Aktifkan eksekusi kode"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2785,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2798
msgid ""
"Exercise great caution with granting code execution privileges. Enable them "
"sparingly and only for trusted roles or ideally only specific users. Grant "
"the least permissions necessary to maintain tight security."
msgstr ""
"Berhati-hatilah saat memberikan hak akses eksekusi kode. Aktifkan secara "
"hemat dan hanya untuk peran yang terpercaya atau idealnya hanya untuk "
"pengguna tertentu. Berikan izin seminimal mungkin untuk menjaga keamanan "
"yang ketat."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2787,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2800
msgid ""
"Function names called through the \"echo\" tag must be whitelisted via the "
"%s filter."
msgstr ""
"Nama fungsi yang dipanggil melalui tag “echo” harus dimasukkan dalam daftar "
"putih melalui filter %s."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2789,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2802
msgid "User roles with code execution capability"
msgstr "Peran pengguna dengan kemampuan eksekusi kode"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2818,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2831
msgid "Individual users with code execution capability"
msgstr "Pengguna individu dengan kemampuan eksekusi kode"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2836,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2849
msgid ""
"Set code execution capability for individual users by editing their user "
"profile."
msgstr ""
"Atur kemampuan eksekusi kode untuk pengguna individu dengan mengedit profil "
"pengguna mereka."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2849,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2862
msgid ""
"Code that requires execution only runs when it has a valid code signature."
msgstr ""
"Kode yang memerlukan eksekusi hanya berjalan ketika memiliki tanda tangan "
"kode yang valid."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2850,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2863
msgid ""
"Regenerate code signatures whenever your WordPress salts (secret keys) "
"change."
msgstr ""
"Buat ulang tanda tangan kode setiap kali salt WordPress (kunci rahasia) Anda "
"berubah."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2854,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2867
msgid ""
"Please create a full-site backup and perform a \"Code review\" (see above) "
"before generating code signatures globally."
msgstr ""
"Harap buat cadangan situs lengkap dan lakukan “Peninjauan kode” (lihat di "
"atas) sebelum membuat tanda tangan kode secara global."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2862,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2875
msgid ""
"Valid code signatures are required for all Code (element), SVG (element) and "
"Query editor instances to run."
msgstr ""
"Tanda tangan kode yang valid diperlukan untuk semua instansi Code (elemen), "
"SVG (elemen), dan Query editor agar dapat berjalan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2867,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2880
msgid "Regenerate code signatures"
msgstr "Buat ulang tanda tangan kode"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2887,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2900
msgid ""
"Custom CSS and JavaScript added below are loaded on your entire website."
msgstr ""
"CSS dan JavaScript kustom yang ditambahkan di bawah ini dimuat di seluruh "
"situs web Anda."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2887,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2900
msgid "Use the builder to add custom code to a specific page."
msgstr "Gunakan pembangun untuk menambahkan kode kustom ke halaman tertentu."

