msgstr "Skrip body (footer)"

#. translators: %s = </body> tag
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2951,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2964
msgid "Footer scripts are added right before closing %s tag."
msgstr "Skrip footer ditambahkan tepat sebelum menutup tag %s."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2983,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2996
msgid "Disable WooCommerce builder"
msgstr "Nonaktifkan pembangun WooCommerce"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2989,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3002
msgid "Enable Bricks WooCommerce \"Notice\" element"
msgstr "Aktifkan elemen “Pemberitahuan” WooCommerce Bricks"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2990,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3003
msgid ""
"You have to add the \"Notice\" element yourself wherever necessary as all "
"native WooCommerce notices are removed when this setting is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus menambahkan elemen “Pemberitahuan” sendiri di mana pun diperlukan "
"karena semua pemberitahuan WooCommerce asli dihapus ketika pengaturan ini "
"diaktifkan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2996,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3009
msgid "Enable Bricks WooCommerce \"Checkout coupon\" element"
msgstr "Aktifkan elemen “Kupon checkout” WooCommerce Bricks"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2997,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3010
msgid ""
"You have to add the \"Checkout coupon\" element yourself on the Checkout "
"page as the native WooCommerce checkout coupon is removed when this setting "
"is enabled. The \"Enable the use of coupon codes\" WooCommerce setting under "
"\"General\" must be active."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus menambahkan elemen “Kupon checkout” sendiri di halaman Checkout "
"karena kupon checkout WooCommerce asli dihapus ketika pengaturan ini "
"diaktifkan. Pengaturan WooCommerce “Aktifkan penggunaan kode kupon” di bawah "
"“Umum” harus aktif."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3003,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3016
msgid "Enable Bricks WooCommerce \"Checkout login\" element"
msgstr "Aktifkan elemen “Login checkout” WooCommerce Bricks"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3004,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3017
msgid ""
"You have to add the \"Checkout login\" element yourself on the Checkout page "
"as the native WooCommerce checkout login is removed when this setting is "
"enabled. The \"Enable log-in during checkout\" WooCommerce setting under "
"\"Accounts & Privacy\" must be active."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus menambahkan elemen “Login checkout” sendiri di halaman Checkout "
"karena login checkout WooCommerce asli dihapus ketika pengaturan ini "
"diaktifkan. Pengaturan WooCommerce “Aktifkan log-in saat checkout” di bawah "
"“Akun & Privasi” harus aktif."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3010,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3023
msgid "Show quantity input field in product loop"
msgstr "Tampilkan kolom input jumlah di loop produk"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3011,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3024
msgid "Only applicable for purchasable simple products with in stock status."
msgstr ""
"Hanya berlaku untuk produk sederhana yang dapat dibeli dengan status stok "
"tersedia."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:3017,
